Friday, August 17, 2007
Garbage Pail Kid Generator. Garbage Pail Kids is a series of trading cards produced by the Topps Company, originally released in 1985. Each sticker card featured a Garbage Pail Kid character, with some comical abnormality or suffering some terrible fate, and a humorous, word play-rich character name.
Now you can make your own Garbage Pail Kid. You have to register first but you can type in anything you want and you don't have to give your email address. I created this Garbage Pail Kid.
